              +-----","---+  +-Fifo----+
   >>-STRING(-+-----------+--+---------+-)---------<<
              +-delimiter-+  +-,-order-+

   Returns a string object that concatenates the string values of the collected
   item objects, using the delimiter string to delimit them, in the specified order.

